WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:08.574 --> 00:00:13.574
400g Patent flour

00:00:15.171 --> 00:00:20.171
100g coarse semolina

00:00:21.333 --> 00:00:26.333
7g instant yeast

00:00:27.571 --> 00:00:32.571
3/4 tablespoon salt

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:46.640
Gradually add the 700ml lukewarm water

00:00:47.594 --> 00:00:55.594
Mix it for about 5 more minutes

00:01:01.288 --> 00:01:06.288
Let is rise for 45 minutes

00:01:07.838 --> 00:01:12.838
After 45 minutes you have to stir the dough curtly

00:01:14.874 --> 00:01:19.874
Let the pan heat up

00:01:24.496 --> 00:01:32.496
Cool it under cold water and dry it with a cloth

00:01:40.122 --> 00:01:48.120
Spoon the mixture into the pan directly

00:01:57.824 --> 00:02:05.820
Turn the heat on high heat

00:02:15.968 --> 00:02:23.970
If the batter is almost dry turn the heat to the lowest setting

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:30.960
When it is completely dry, let it get golden brown on the bottom

00:02:31.300 --> 00:02:36.300
Grease it with olive oil or melted butter

00:02:37.169 --> 00:02:45.170
Repeat the staps

